      "title": "Sri Lanka: CEYPETCO & Lanka IOC Fuel Prices Increased",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st): The Ceylon Petroleum Corporation announced that\u00a0CEYPETCO fuel prices have been increased with effect from 2 AM on Sunday (26). At the same time Lanka IOC also announced that it increased its fuel prices following the CPC price revision.",
        "High-Level US Treasury Dept & State Dept delegation in Sri Lanka",
        "Fuel shipments further delayed & CPC cannot confirm next shipment arrival date"
